author: James Walker
title: Alex Jones Shakes Hands With Protesters at Texas Rally to Reopen State Against Stay-at-Home Orders
description: The Infowars founder also called the COVID-19 pandemic shutdowns a "21st Century war" as he addressed the Austin rally.
content:
The conspiracy theorist Alex Jones was pictured shaking hands with protesters at a Texas rally against social distancing measures on Saturday.
A video posted on Twitter yesterday showed the Infowars founder shaking hands with at least four people at the demo… [+5507 chars]
